      "content": "ok but if the \"consensus\" is that they're mostly bad, doesn't that mean including the \"national security\" stuff is just an excuse to keep using outdated policies? like, if the math says they hurt the economy, isn't it more accurate to say they're just a mistake rather than a \"tool\"?",
